On November 25, 2020, St. Michael’s Hospital assembled a panel of medical experts from St. Michael’s Hospital @UnityHealth to provide answers and advice regarding pregnancy and birth during these unique pandemic times. The 1-hour panel includes our very own Dr. @talibogler, as well as Dr. @dougcampbenll3672 (neonatologist and NICU director), Dr. Filomena Meffe (Chief of Obstetrics) and Dr. Julie Maggi (psychiatrist in perinatal mental health). 

*Please note: This panel was recorded on November 25, 2020. Local case numbers as well as Public Health Guidelines have since changed since the recording of this video and therefore general advice given may no longer be applicable. Please ensure you are making informed decisions that reflect your current local Public Health guidelines. 

Below are time stamps that you can use to learn about specific topics: 

